					<h4 class="header-admission">Step One - Online Application</h4>
					<br>
					<h6>Please be ready to upload the following documents:</h6>
					<ul>
						<li>Copy of your child’s most recent nursery or school report (for KG1 and up)</li>
						<li>Copy of your child’s passport (first page and Visa) and Emirates ID (front and back), if
							already available</li>
						<li>Copy of both parents passports (first page and Visa) and Emirates ID (front and back), if
							already available</li>
						<li>Copy of a passport sized photograph of your child</li>
						<li>Copy of any learning difficulty diagnostic testing or educational assessment (if applicable)
							*</li>
						<li>Copy of any psychological assessments (if applicable) *</li>
						<li>Copy of custody papers (if applicable)</li>
					</ul>


					<h4 class="header-admission">Step Two - Interview and Assessment</h4>

					<ol>
						<li>Once the fully completed application with complete documents has been received,
							Admissions request confidential Teacher Recommendation from student’s
							former school for applicants G2 and above.</li>
						<li>Applicant invited to interview and assessment (Sunday through Thursday 9am to 4pm).
							Please pay the non-refundable application fee of AED 525
							(check, cash or credit card) when you come to the assessment.</li>
					</ol>

					<h4 class="header-admission">Step Three - Interview and Assessment </h4>
					<ol>
						<li>Once the fully completed application with complete documents has been received,
							Admissions request confidential Teacher Recommendation from student’s former school for
